OL,6,FNow, in a major development, the
OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,8,Fconfirmed the government is
OL,9,Fconsidering enhanced cancer screening
OL,10,Ffor those impacted by the use of
OL,11,FStilbestrol, also known as DES, and
OL,12,Fhas vowed to "look seriously at these
OL,13,Fallegations."
OL,15,FWhat is DES?
OL,17,FStilbestrol, also known as DES, was
OL,18,Fprescribed on the NHS to prevent
OL,19,Fmiscarriage and to stop breast milk
OL,20,Fproduction from 1939 until the late
OL,21,F1970s.
