OL,6,FOther countries around the world, such
OL,7,Fas the United States, banned the drug
OL,8,Fin the 1970s as scientific studies
OL,9,Flinked the use of DES with breast,
OL,10,Fcervical, and vaginal cancers. In the
OL,11,FUK, health authorities failed to do
OL,12,Fthe same.
OL,14,FThe UK government claimed that in
OL,15,F1973, a letter was sent to all doctors
OL,16,Ftelling them to stop using DES for pre-
OL,17,Fmenopausal women, but ITV News has
OL,18,Ffound dozens of women who say they
OL,19,Fwere given it after that date, some as
OL,20,Flate as 1980.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
