OL,6,FIn 1971, US scientists proved DES was
OL,7,Funsafe for use on pre-menopausal
OL,8,Fwomen. The medicines watchdog, the
OL,9,FMHRA, repeatedly told ITV News that in
OL,10,FMay 1973, "the Committee on Safety of
OL,11,FMedicines wrote to all doctors to
OL,12,Fadvise against the use of DES in
OL,13,Fpregnancy and women who have not yet
OL,14,Fgone through menopause."
OL,16,FNo evidence of that letter can be
OL,17,Ffound. A series of Freedom of
OL,18,FInformation requests and internal
OL,19,Freviews from ITV News to the MHRA were
OL,20,Frejected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
