OL,6,FOur team has searched through hundreds
OL,7,Fof pages of public health records at
OL,8,Fthe British Library and National
OL,9,FArchives, and there is no evidence of
OL,10,Fthat 1973 letter.
OL,12,FIn fact, there is no evidence to show
OL,13,Fthat DES was withdrawn or restricted,
OL,14,Fdespite mounting evidence of the
OL,15,Fdrug's sinister side effects.
